Class LimitedSourcePath

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.modern.LimitedSourcePath
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourcePath, Comparable<SourcePath>

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
 @Generated(value={"Immutables.generator","AbstractLimitedSourcePath"})
 @Immutable
 @CheckReturnValue
public final class LimitedSourcePath
extends Object
    This can be passed around as a SourcePath, but it can only be resolved by InputPathResolver's LimitedSourcePathResolver. This is just meant to be used for interacting with old-style Steps that take in SourcePath and resolvers.
